k glasses and a blue tracksuit as he blows out smoke rings in the same colour as the iconic Olympic rings.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the background, the Eiffel Tower can be seen below an etching of the word Paris.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2770, \"end\": 2775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.572317978131173e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Starsky and Hutch star, whose real name is Calvin Broadus Jr, showed off the pin as he handed it over to US tennis star Coco Gauff in an exchange on Instagram.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2825, \"end\": 2839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Calvin Broadus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"score\": 0.8662909163437968, \"rank\": 0.08149461857105773, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\"}, {\"begin\": 2902, \"end\": 2912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}, {\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.378188671289859e-40, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http